Cloud computing is the methodology where you can create or build any machines or applications on a particular platform that can be accessed from anywhere at anytime.

Deploying Models of applications
1.Private 
2.Public
3.Hybrid

---> Imagine you are an azure architect and you have to create a linux machine that is ubuntu LTS either 16.04 or 18.04 in US based region. You have to print your own name that contains a html file with the image of Quark and that image or the whole file will be accessed through a page block. How can you achieve the whole process with the azure portal.
